Definition: having or fostering a warm or friendly and informal atmosphere
Example: had a cozy chat; a relaxed informal manner; an intimate cocktail lounge; the small room was cozy and intimate
Synonyms: noun, state, coziness, intimate, informal, attribute, informality, having, or, fostering, a, warm, friendly, and, atmosphere, had, chat, relaxed, manner, an, cocktail, lounge, the, small, room, was
Category: adj.all
